{"tid":409823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發!!! 方力申成功追回Stephy 表示儲錢希望2018年內娶Stephy","createTime":"2017-09-22T11:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T05:09:16.000Z","uid":30873,"like":51,"dislike":345,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0b698fac9f0b02a22dce097a2237092314405b","tid":409823,"uid":30873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">(突發獨家) 成功追回Stephy ，方力申表示儲錢希望2018年內娶Stephy</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/192803_950462369a269e9820ff72e3060a76ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F192803_950462369a269e9820ff72e3060a76ac.jpg&h=5bf9c6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/192804_0c88f5cfc996e6bad826b65742405e09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F192804_0c88f5cfc996e6bad826b65742405e09.jpg&h=adfd5c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小方因新劇受阻而損失過百萬，令他感無奈。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他大呻因劇本題材敏感而被抽起，對於開新劇受阻，他感嘆：「唉，原本12月就開戲，不過呢行成日都係咁，無辦法啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/193240_23feca46fb0d69b8e9881c1e63615093.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F193240_23feca46fb0d69b8e9881c1e63615093.jpg&h=f8100011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n方力申昨日到電台錄音，被問及與前女友鄧麗欣（Stephy）有否計劃復合，小方說：「我地有可能再一齊生活，已經口頭計劃係2018年結婚，依家努力賺錢儲老婆本，而且將來一定會生小朋友。」小方更透露由於最近經濟不景，加上準備開拍的內地電視劇突然叫停，導致他損失逾百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n對於會否和Stephy一起再在幕前証明復合，他卻表示各有各忙，加上未來可能會做更多主持，也許要幾星期先再見佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/192902_f6b26fdb5bd3eeb53a90371f68b453ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F192902_f6b26fdb5bd3eeb53a90371f68b453ec.jpg&h=00b16747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方力申儲老婆本娶Stephy<br />\n<br />\n方力申昨日到電台錄音時透露支持球隊阿仙奴，問到女友鄧麗欣（Stephy）日前指37歲前要結婚？小方回應：「咁都要儲老婆本，買樓、生小朋友都要用錢！（Stephy 37歲前結？）唔係！係我38歲前！（仲有幾耐？）一年咋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/192930_7fde78b60f945bd470d1ec46d9878857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F192930_7fde78b60f945bd470d1ec46d9878857.jpg&h=2e540214&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/192947_15252a2e2f243a2aa96e5895e13eec88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F192947_15252a2e2f243a2aa96e5895e13eec88.jpg&h=69eba39f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://funstory.org/-xinpolu/n/8480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffunstory.org%2F-xinpolu%2Fn%2F8480&d=zO%2FjE4h7bd6oxmBH%2BWRXN6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b5d6f005\" target=\"_blank\">https://funstory.org/-xinpolu/n/8480</a>"},{"pid":"28a21bfdca011b27ba9e8b0c2b3be3b135b97aa7","tid":409823,"uid":40470,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"ce32ad72a00b29e1eca4f064f9fd7510f6d45d0a","tid":409823,"uid":42217,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"957f7b7de96c6122206b7c1264d1ba7170ae4567","tid":409823,"uid":30873,"like":907,"dislike":110,"score":797,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想佢地復合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好馬不吃回頭草</span>"},{"pid":"f6519d95d4777841ae90322a22f8eb72e3a43f38","tid":409823,"uid":15658,"like":13,"dislike":55,"score":-42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:37:26.000Z","msg":"超蓮唔要要個老女人"},{"pid":"84b7ee9428c3b72235999a493821cf2ea67cc5d7","tid":409823,"uid":52942,"like